very sorry' after breakdancing was mocked following her appearance in Paris.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9305582555787136, \"rank\": 0.07272296860793546, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999798019419, \"rank\": 2.019816256327724e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her appearance\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is really sad to hear those criticisms,' she said.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those criticisms\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I am very sorry for the backlash that the community has experienced, but I can not control how people react.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Unfortunately, we just need some more resources in Australia for us to have a chance to be world champions.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some more resources\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"Australia\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"world champions\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In the last year, I have trained my hardest.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []